snippet.textDisplay: This is pure nostalgic Pakistani music of 90's as well as coke studio of RH era . This is the only example from CS 14 & 15 so far where just the song, lyrics and music arrangement have overwhelmed the brilliant visuals. This is why this is the most impactful music in these two seasons. In a way, I can interpret this as an ode to RH and the 90's era of Pakistani music. Pure magic.
